{"tid":995733,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"［新番］黃汝敏 你條8婆好還錢! (2) 之追數行動組","createTime":"2019-01-25T16:27:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-07T05:21:55.000Z","uid":223016,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0336ed533755c935149121abd9fd26af25902482","tid":995733,"uid":223016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T16:27:27.000Z","msg":"舊post <br />\n<br />\n黃汝敏 你條8婆好還錢！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/994251\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/994251</a><br />\n<br />\n因為有巴打要求開新post <br />\n基於舊post完左<br />\n真係估唔到一日就完左post<br />\n<br />\n首先整返個懶人包先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BxqgCt1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBxqgCt1.png&h=3fa613ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說故事就係咁既<br />\n<br />\n有一個叫黃汶敏既人唔還錢<br />\n<br />\n呢個故事會繼續跟進追討黃汶敏還錢既行動<br />\n<br />\n因為樓主要採取實質行動 所以未必下下即時回應大家<br />\n<br />\n同時追債行動會同大家報導 黃汝敏如果對樓主採取正面回應既態度 或者 已還錢 樓主會通報各位"},{"pid":"9a767610ab0943881152887869fc6ff5ee27fb90","tid":995733,"uid":223016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T16:29:28.000Z","msg":"又要出新post 屌"},{"pid":"783f26d9772c530a8e72d18e65cd7b58bcca12a2","tid":995733,"uid":230890,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T16:30:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"26036c80e6701a5e6394b3cf3b4b604f82f39193","tid":995733,"uid":223016,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"783f26d9772c530a8e72d18e65cd7b58bcca12a2","tid":995733,"uid":230890,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T16:30:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T16:33:10.000Z","msg":"多謝<br />\n<br />\n講個消息<br />\n<br />\n最新一期既單張會有QR code 直接去舊post"},{"pid":"3e9ee5976b3fc565368d14e2ff8bc096624edd93","tid":995733,"uid":232874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T16:43:18.000Z","msg":"寄咗啲證據去佢公司未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":